{"title":"New Focus VAM2 SL eMTB dips under 32lbs!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/new-focus-vam2-sl-emtb-dips-under-32lbs/","date":1707311301000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action.jpg\" alt=\"rider on a focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-riding-action-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>The new Focus VAM<sup>2</sup> introduces an entirely new suspension design to their e-bike lineup. A new motor and full carbon frame save weight and give them new kinematics to play with for a poppy short travel platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Their current touring-oriented Thron<sup>2</sup> model uses a VPP design, and the JAM<sup>2</sup> and SAM<sup>2</sup> use an alloy Horst Link design. The VAM<sup>2</sup> SL switches to a carbon fiber rear triangle with no rear pivot and flex seatstays. This combo brings the claimed frame weight as low as 2,172g (4.79lbs) for the top spec, and a complete bike weight <em>under</em> 32 pounds!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Frame details &amp; tech</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1.jpg\" alt=\"focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike shown from the side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-1-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike shown from the side\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike shown from the side\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A smaller battery and Fazua’s tiny Ride 60 motor combine with the sleek rear end for a bike that looks very much like an analog bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 430Wh battery should give you plenty of juice, but you can add their 210Wh range extender and plug it in while riding to extend play time. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>An integrated mud flap keeps gunk from wedging between the chainstay yoke and BB shell, and frame protection wrap protects the carbon and finish, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-10-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can pair the Fazua system with your cycling computer to display cadence and power (as in, your power output in watts). It also pairs with their own app so you can customize the motor’s output per setting.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-5-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Focus VAM<sup>2</sup> SL gets 125mm rear wheel travel with a stout main pivot and thick chainstays and yoke to keep it torsionally stiff. Up front are 130mm forks, but it’s compatible with 140mm forks, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-9-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-6-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>The bike comes with a frame protection sticker set you can apply if you want. (Photos c. Focus Bicycles)</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /><figcaption>The bike comes with a frame protection sticker set you can apply if you want. (Photos c. Focus Bicycles)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /><figcaption>The bike comes with a frame protection sticker set you can apply if you want. (Photos c. Focus Bicycles)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The seatstays are flattened, allowing them to flex as the suspension compresses. These types of pivot-free rear ends typically provide a snappier feel.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-8-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The battery display is flat on the top tube, but the power button is integrated into the mode dial on the handlebar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All cables run through the headset, entering a port under the stem. Split spacers keep it easy to adjust stack height. The top two models (9.9 &amp; 9.0) get Focus’s new 290g one-piece bar stem.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-23.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of the new focus vam2 sl e-mountain bike\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of focus vam2 sl\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-7.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of focus vam2 sl\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"closeup details of focus vam2 sl\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>An integrated chain keeper and removable motor cover (which doubles as impact protection) come standard.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Geometry &amp; pricing</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"851\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart-297x126.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart-800x340.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart-120x51.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart-768x327.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/FOCUS-VAM2-SL-eMTB-geometry-chart-1536x654.jpg 1536w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>An adjustable head angle lets you tune it for the trails at hand. Swapping to a 140mm fork will slacken the head angle by 0.5º.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete bikes top out at €10,999 for the top VAM2 SL 9.0 model with a claimed weight of just 16.2kg (31.75lb). The 9.9 (€8,699, 17.5kg) and 9.8 (€6,899, 18.4kg) sit below that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The 8.9 (€5,799) model uses a lower level carbon for a 2,545g (5.61lb) frame weight and 19.1kg complete bike weight. Full specs for all models on their website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ride.focus.bike/VAM2SL\" target=\"_blank\">Ride.Focus.Bike</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-focus-vam2-sl-emtb-dips-under-32lbs/\">New Focus VAM2 SL eMTB dips under 32lbs!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"6feaeca726c919cea1435333127bc93a916288037219490cb42e97fbb41430ac","category":"Cycling"}